
   Debian-scpecific configuration
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


When you start vifm for the first time, a subdirectory ~/.vifm is created
with a personal config file vifmrc0.2 and a Trash folder. You should edit
the configuration file to match your preferences.


   Vim configuration:

This package automatically installs and compiles its helptags. Just start
vim and try ":h vifm". The vifm.vim plugin is also installed, see the
plugin section in the helpfile for commands.
